title: How to unsubscribe from Magisterium AI Projector
description: Learn how to cancel your Magisterium AI Projector subscription. Follow these steps to manage your subscription and avoid future charges.

steps_1.title: Unsubscribe via Google Play Store
steps_1.description:
* Open the Google Play Store app on your Android device.
* Tap on your profile icon in the top right corner.
* Select 'Payments & subscriptions'.
* Tap on 'Subscriptions'.
* Find 'Magisterium AI Projector' in the list of your subscriptions.
* Tap on 'Magisterium AI Projector'.
* Tap 'Cancel subscription'.
* Follow the on-screen instructions to confirm the cancellation.
